{"tid":1816652,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「二手資料」滙豐銀行請左退休狗番去守分行 一日$2000人工","createTime":"2020-01-08T11:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T11:46:08.000Z","uid":69416,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"65d0fa05df0a9b12812ee9f8c26594f40852de63","tid":1816652,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:37:35.000Z","msg":"二手資料 來源屋企人<br />\n目前滙豐銀行請左退休狗守分行<br />\n已知有中環總行等<br />\n反而旺角附近好似就無<br />\n<br />\n據消息指<br />\n特勤小隊一日番12個鐘<br />\n每一個鐘會係分行出面兜個圈巡邏<br />\n巡完就番入去on99坐 無野做<br />\n但係一日就袋$2000<br />\n合約做到一月月底<br />\n<br />\n由於係二手資料 所以證明唔到D咩<br />\n希望上面資料幫到手足出街做運動<br />\n<br />\n題外話 滙豐應該全面淪陷 <br />\n涉及與全港最大恐怖組織有利益輸送關係 <br />\n大家可以唔法再比面就撚住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b32cecae9fa8e35ad5ed6fff6ed833d8687bcef","tid":1816652,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:37:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"22462b9c9ac4899d39e7bb533c597326c56364b9","tid":1816652,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:38:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8889225a54fde9187351c6dc480e18da238473bd","tid":1816652,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:38:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"818a5ca6d0101f476833a39a1a5f8a86e5e84e3c","tid":1816652,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:38:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a826fb3d47b34cd25ba988e3a6583cdbb042d12","tid":1816652,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:39:07.000Z","msg":"其實係咪已經係old news"},{"pid":"e96f42c231336b2bf56ec03c2cf9a0baad70b671","tid":1816652,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:39:12.000Z","msg":"港大都有"},{"pid":"52c65f1bfe970e528c2a6bd04c09aaf16d8458f5","tid":1816652,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma